<dl id="n42018a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42018a">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42018a"> 18(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> he fled away</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">&ldquo;The priests are the husbands of the nuns, and the lay brothers of the lay sisters. In the chamber of one of the nuns I have mentioned a man was one day found; he fled away, but, soon after, they gave him to us as our confessor extraordinary. <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 75</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c09133d" href="c09all.htm#c09133d">VI.C.09:133(d)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
